verse.lines:
{lang-eng}Though we may waver, He remaineth steadfast,
And all His words are sure;
From everlasting unto everlasting,
His promises endure.{/lang-eng}

{lang-eng}Though we may wander, He will not forsake us,
Truer than earthly friend;
He never fails our trust, for having loved us,
He loves unto the end.{/lang-eng}

{lang-eng}Unto the end; we doubt Him, we deny Him,
We wound Him, we forget;
We get some earthly idol up between us,
Without one faint regret.{/lang-eng}
